imdb.plot outline: Danny Lenko's Playboy Tv show has come to an end and Danny has decided to move on..and out, of his parents house and all the way to L.A. But Danny's goals are no longer to make adult films but instead to cross over into mainstream. But, as Danny finds out, its a lot harder to do than he ever expected and his move to L.A might not be as permanent as he first thought.
